<p>
<lb n="1"/><note n="382-1">This is the continuation of No. 1134 below. The order given in the<hi rend="italic">Annual Report</hi> is followed.</note> <unclear>ṇī</unclear>nāthaśikhaṇḍamaṇḍanamaṇēḥ kōdaṇḍagāṇḍīvinā śrīkhaṇḍāmṛtapiṇḍapāṇḍuyaśasō <gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/><unclear>vakṣaḥ</unclear>phīṭhagapuṇḍarīkanilayādgo<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>k<unclear>kā</unclear>nmahāśāṁkkarādyassaṁprāpya cirāya naṁdati jagat khyātādva <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] śākābdē kha<unclear>mu</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nidyucaṁdragaṇitē sūryyōparāgē madhau māsē sōyamadānmudā guṇagaṇāvāsō vaṇigrāmaṇī<unclear>ḥ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> dyumaṇisthi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>radaśaṁ pōtaḥ pratītaḥ kṣitau dākṣārāmanivāsinē bhagavatē bhīmāya dīpaṁ kṛtī [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] śakavarṣa 1070 <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> śrāhi Uttarā<unclear>ya</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṇasaṁkrānti nimittamuna śrīmaṇmahāmaṇḍalēśvara kulōttuṁ<supplied reason="omitted">ga</supplied>cōḍagoṁkkarājula seṭṭi penuṁgo <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> lagōtra bhīmise<unclear>ṭṭi</unclear>
<lb n="6"/>koḍku bhaṇḍanabhīma pōtiseṭṭi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍavartti lōhadaṇḍu di <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <unclear>drā</unclear>rkkamu neyi sari
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yiṁccuvārugā bōlu naluvuruṁ būṇṭagā reṇḍavu <supplied reason="omitted">naḍapuna</supplied>bādabōla Eṟiyani Aḍapuna manavabhōla <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <unclear>vasa</unclear>munaṁ beṭṭina I
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nupaEḍlu 50 ṇṭiki nityapaḍi golavaṁgala tribhuvanāṁkkuśa nēmāna 1 ṇḍu likitaṁ sūrācāryya <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

